Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the aftermath of the tears lies a cheesecake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to catch the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we'll need Japanese, English, and German!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our usual group went to see the Tokyo Spirits soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the Spirits lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We then parked to get our food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:28.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And then, when we returned, a German man we\Nhad met earlier named Ludger had been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:28.03,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ludger Heinen (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To our surprise, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said "criminal" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pointed at Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.79,0:02:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gave us all a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.21,0:02:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he fainted, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said: "Criminal".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.60,0:02:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he latched onto my shoulder and muttered, "El."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,El...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the criminal has some connection with both Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whatever it is that "El" refers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanna know why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to tell you police officers that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:47.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I don't have time for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:55.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, bot someone was attacked here and you\Nthree are the only ones that were in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We ask you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:01.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What? Where's the proof? You can't hold us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:07.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if you refuse now, we'll come to your home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:51.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inagaki Hiramasa (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Genda Tatsuzou (44)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:04:01.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kojima Kanji (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was listening to the horse race in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The off-track waging office is in here, so if I won,\NI planned to go collect and then go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kojima Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kojima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you have the same last name as Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number on your shirt is the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide from the Tokyo Spirits wears the number 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is wearing a Tokyo Spirits shirt right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, the Spirits also have the quick Naoki on their team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we always called him "Genta" in front\Nof Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and never used "Kojima", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:15.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, since he wasn't aware his family name is\N"Kojima," that can't be why he pointed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're next. Why were you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to buy a bag for my girl, but they don't sell it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was trying to hurry and get to the next store,\Nbut some guy was there fixing the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, what a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Genda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Genta!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Genda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda Tatsuzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're implying, but I'm not "Genta".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably misheard you as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're fat, just like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's foolish, there are plenty of fat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor and Inspector Megure, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be different if Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knew these\Nthree were the only suspects, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt think he'd leave such an oblivious hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, after Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed to Genta\Nand said, "Criminal", he also said "El".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knew his name, wouldn't he have just said "Genda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally you. Why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came to see the press event for the idol\NSakaguchi Ai on the sixth floor of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Inagaki Hiromasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his driver's license, the kanji he uses for\N"Hiromasa" can also be used for "Taishou", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:52.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,INAGAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:55.13,Signs,,0,0,0,,GAKIDAISHO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you took out the "Ina" kanji from your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Neighborhood Kids Leader"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just said Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doesn't know the criminal's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's too convenient to be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And also, look at his hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a big "L" on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Official Sakaguchi Ai merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that "L" either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were referring to that hat, he would\Nhave said "love" instead of "El-".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with him being German, maybe he couldn't read it..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His previous wife was British, meaning he can speak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would have definitely read L-O-V-E as "love".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,KARAI\NSPICEY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:44.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,TSURAI\NTRING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,OSATSU\NBILL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:48.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,OFUDA\NLABEL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like Japanese where "karai" can be "tsurai" and\N"osatsu" can be "ofuda". (Spicy -> Tiring, Bill -> Label)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:08:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's a word in both German and English\Nthat's spelled the same, but has different meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? That relates to his message?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His message was about another mischiveous boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:14.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When can we get outta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only here by chance, why should I have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the press event will be over soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but, we need to get your stories first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my car listening to the horse race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said earlier, I came here to get that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, they don't even sell the damn bag here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry off to the event and get a god seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anybody get attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:09:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You three are saying that all three of you just happened to be\Nhere at the time, and yet none of you saw anything suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what we're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that means we're free to leave, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, what about that fat kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy pointed to him and said "criminal", didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean this boy did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was down here kicking that ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:32.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, isn't it more likely he accidentally kicked the ball and hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta isn't the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, are we done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} couldn't be the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to say that Genta had something in\Ncommon with the one who attacked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because just like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the culprit was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:04.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a serious assault, not some mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I refer to is the very image.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inagaki Hiromasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you came for an idol's press event, you must have a camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, you're a camera kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A camera kid and a mischevious boy are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, they could be the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make this guy the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he pulled a lot of pranks as a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does that make me the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:11:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, how would Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nknow how his childhood went?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves us with this Genda guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he looks more like a bad guy than someone into mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He actually does seem bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on a moment. That's not what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, could you please explain now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't Japanese, it's English...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The small fairies that appear in fantasy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fairies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The title "elf" can applied to a small kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's also another application which means a "mischevious boy".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:12:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he said "El" after pointing to Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was trying to say "elf "!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how does that relate to Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true that Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looks like the most mischevious,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a small fairy or elf should've been Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from when Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} kicked a soccer\Nball in here and hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Genta did it, he called him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A naughty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to say that the criminal was an elf like Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A criminal elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. The hint was to say the criminal was mischevious, like an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.87,0:12:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see him saying that about Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine any of these three as a small, prank loving fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you explain it, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I failed to mention earlier that Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is German\Nand can speak German, English, and Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when they asked who did it, the numbers\Nin his native language came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eiens, zwei, drei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, in German, we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One is "eiens"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two is "zwei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three is "drei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four is "vier"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five is "funf"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six is "sechs"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven is "sieben"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eight is "acht"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nine is "neun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten is "zehn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And eleven is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Elf."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima Kanji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the number on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and tried to say\N"eleven" and "elf", to give a German and English hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his knowledge of a Germany and\NEngland, he went to Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, he hoped the Professor\Nwould be able to figure out its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he knew Japanese, wouldn't it be easier\Nto have just said "eleven" in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably did that on purpose, just in case the\Ncriminal were still nearby and saw us talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was afraid we would get attacked if we knew anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be joking, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what this elf thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why am I automatically the criminal for wearing the #11?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, that German guy didn't even\Nget to completely say "elf", did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is all of your reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his reasoning seems perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seemed confident back there, Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Japanese, not some stupid elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think he's right, show me some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, some proof that shows I'm the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of you saw me hit that foreigner and run away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like no one here can prove I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:41.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this man named Kojima hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I found Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} covered in\Nblood, I saw this man running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys seen him too, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys seen him too, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't let him just say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you testify to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't let him lie to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find this a bit strange!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he saw me then, wouldn't he have said so from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just playing along with what that old bastard said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just made it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, we've known Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for awhile now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's honest enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you insane!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you not see he's making this up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even saw the number on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you... If you don't shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him! I saw him! I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was the first one to find Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you got that, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you messed up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember? The first to find him was the fat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Genta was the first to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did we tell them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! I saw this kid by himself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was playing soccer by himself, earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were listening to horse racing\Nin your car and didn't hear Genta scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't hear him scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know he was first to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him kicking the ball by himself, so assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I couldn't hear anything, I could've just looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you know it was Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just kicking the ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd know, because at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with the steel pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw this soccer ball come by and you knew, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew Genta, who was kicking the\Nball around, would come looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really was listening to the horse race!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the horse that won the main race today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were listening to the horse races, you'd have to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we came back during the main race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't expect you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s ball came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to hurry out of the parking lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only to realize that the broken gate was being\Nrepaired and Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:20:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you hid in your car to avoid the police and pretended\Nto have been listening to the horse race the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:07.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your heart was pounding and your mind was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard, you're not getting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at least now you'll know some of the pain you've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.82,0:22:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the criminal did it just for the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.03,0:22:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what Officer Takagi said when he called the\NProfessor earlier to thank him for solving the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was apparently on the run from loan sharks and got desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:36.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Japan's crimes are being more and more Americanized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wasn't the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had lost all reason to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was pretty cruel of that foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.81,0:22:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pointing at a kid and saying "criminal".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really was, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta could have really become a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These little detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:06.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything OK with your head injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this that German?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this as a gift, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is cheesecake from that store!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.69,0:23:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is very thoughtful of you, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.32,0:23:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Why did such a weak horse have to win!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This race should've been in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:23:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the strong one that wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:55.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that wins is strong!
